    "raw_proof_text": "# THE TORSIONAL TREFOIL MARKOV PUMP THEOREM (TTMPT)\n\n## ABSTRACT\nA formal proof establishing a deterministic framework for a one-way stochastic pump acting on a longitudinal binding-scalar field. The system operates over a 12-channel lattice Hilbert space, breaking detailed balance through a topological 'Tesla-valve' Markovian kernel.\n\n## PHASES\n1. Axiomatic Foundation of $\\mathcal{H}_{12}$\n2. Hilbert-to-Markov Mapping\n3. Detailed Balance Violation\n4. Frame 5 Compression\n5. Pump Stroke Dynamics\n6. Dissipative Toroidal Collapse\n7. Phase Identity Reset",
